---
title: Double Plant-Based Crumbed Chick'n & Chermoula Wedges with Radish Salad & Plant-Based Mayo
description: Who says eating plant-based is boring? It's time to get excited for our crumbed chick'n – we've paired it with herby baked wedges
and a radish salad for maximum flavour and fun. Don't forget the creamy pesto sauce for dipping!
